<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْمَسْأَلَةُ الْأُولَى<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فِيمَا يَنْقُضُ الْعَهْدَ وَمَا لَا يَنْقُضُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَنَحْنُ نَذْكُرُ مَذَاهِبَ الْأَئِمَّةِ وَمَا قَالَهُ أَتْبَاعُهُمْ فِي ذَلِكَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">ذِكْرُ قَوْلِ الْإِمَامِ أَحْمَدَ وَأَصْحَابِهِ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قَدْ ذَكَرْنَا نُصُوصَهُ فِي انْتِقَاضِ الْعَهْدِ بِالزِّنَى بِالْمُسْلِمَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">ذِكْرُ قَوْلِهِ فِي انْتِقَاضِ الْعَهْدِ بِسَبِّ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>قَالَ الْخَلَّالُ <span class="c2">(بَابٌ فِيمَنْ شَتَمَ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>